OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChancellor Rishi Sunak     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdefends likely pensions    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Frise                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Chancellor Rishi Sunak has defended    
OL,6, restoring the triple lock, which could 
OL,7, see pensions rise by 10% in line with  
OL,8, inflation.                             
OL,10,FIt comes as the government warns       
OL,11,Fworkers not to expect pay rises to keep
OL,12,Fpace with increasing costs.            
OL,14,FEconomist and Labour adviser Jim       
OL,15,FO'Neill said the "constant protection  
OL,16,Fof pensioners" was "ludicrous".        
OL,18,FBut Mr Sunak said pensioners were      
OL,19,F"among the most vulnerable in society" 
OL,20,Fand needed to be protected.            
